---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Welcome to Astro.">
	<header>
        <h1>
            <a href="/" aria-label="Coming Soon">
            <span>Coming Soon</span>
            <img src="logo.svg" alt="Coming Soon Template" width="96" height="48">
            </a>
        </h1>
    </header>
    <main>
        <p>There’s lots of ways to be, as a person. And some people express their deep appreciation in different ways. But one of the ways that I believe people express their appreciation to the rest of humanity is to make something wonderful and put it out there.</p>
        <p>We are taking ideas from the personal computer, web browser, and latest in Al, to create a computing experience that's powerful yet delightfully human.</p>
        <p>Announcing <a href="bbb.bot">BBB</a>, a AI platform that help governments, be effecient</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Private, secure data</li>
            <li>Real-time solutions, at your fingertips</li>
            <li>Scalable across agencies</li>
            <li>Empowering voices, simplifying bureaucracy</li>
        </ul>
        <p>We are launching gradually! Stay tuned.</p>
        <figure>
            <img src="/sigg.png" alt="sign" width="90" height="40">
        </figure>
		<!-- EV's signature size is [at] W: 90 & H: 40 && Slijo's signature is [at] W:  -->
        <dl>
            <dt>Voila!</dt>
            <dd>Team BBB</dd>
            <dd><a href="mailto:bonjour@bbb.bot">bonjour@bbb.bot</a></dd>
        </dl>

        <p role="complementary" aria-label="P.S.">
            <strong>P.S.</strong> Join our waiting to fly w/ us!
        </p>

        <section>
        <form name="subscribe-form" target="_self" aria-label="Subscribe"  action="https://formspree.io/f/meojypkb"
  method="POST">
            <aside>
                <fieldset>
                    <input type="email" class="text-input" autocomplete="email" placeholder="Email address" name="EMAIL" tabindex="0">
                    <button class="button" type="submit" name="subscribe" tabindex="-1"> &#8594; </button>
                </fieldset>
            </aside>
        </form>
        </section>

    </main>
</Layout>

<style>
@import "@new-ui/foundations";

*,
*::before,
*::after {
    box-sizing: border-box
}

html,
body,
div,
span,
applet,
button,
input,
select,
textarea,
object,
iframe h1,
h2,
h3,
h4,
h5,
h6,
hr,
p,
blockquote,
pre,
a,
abbr,
acronym,
address,
big,
cite,
code,
del,
dfn,
em,
img,
ins,
kbd,
q,
s,
samp,
small,
strike,
strong,
sub,
sup,
tt,
var,
b,
u,
i,
center,
dl,
dt,
dd,
ol,
ul,
li,
fieldset,
form,
label,
legend,
table,
caption,
tbody,
tfoot,
thead,
tr,
th,
td,
article,
aside,
canvas,
details,
embed,
figure,
figcaption,
footer,
header,
hgroup,
main,
menu,
nav,
output,
ruby,
section,
summary,
time,
mark,
audio,
video {
    background: transparent;
    border: 0;
    font: inherit;
    font-size: 100%;
    margin: 0;
    min-width: 0;
    outline: 0;
    padding: 0;
    vertical-align: baseline
}

article,
aside,
details,
figcaption,
figure,
footer,
header,
hgroup,
main,
menu,
nav,
section,
img,
svg {
    display: block
}

ol,
ul,
menu {
    list-style: none
}

body {
    background: var(--background);
    color: var(--text-primary);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    font-family: var(--transitional);
    font-feature-settings: 'liga', 'dlig';
    -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
    -moz-osx-font-smoothing: grayscale;
    font-size: var(--desktop-body-xl);
    line-height: var(--lh-desktop-body-xl);
    font-style: normal;
    min-height: 100vh;
    text-rendering: optimizeLegibility
}

@supports(-webkit-touch-callout: none) {
    body {
        min-height: -webkit-fill-available
    }
}

header,
main {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    margin-inline: auto;
    width: min(100%, 32em)
}

header {
    height: var(--spacing-16, 6em)
}

header h1 {
    align-items: center;
    display: flex;
    flex: 1;
    justify-content: flex-end
}

header h1 a {
    height: var(--spacing-11, 3em);
    max-width: 5.96em
}

header h1 a span {
    display: none
}

header h1 a img {
    height: 100%;
    max-height: 100%;
    width: auto
}

main {
    flex: 1;
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-15, 5em)
}

main>*+* {
    margin-top: var(--spacing-08, 1.5em)
}

ol,
ul {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column
}

ol li,
ul li {
    position: relative
}

ol li:before,
ul li:before {
    font-feature-settings: 'case', 'tnum';
    left: 0;
    position: absolute;
    top: 0
}

ol {
    counter-reset: counter;
    gap: var(--spacing-02)
}

ol li {
    counter-increment: counter;
    padding-left: var(--spacing-09)
}

ol li:before {
    content: counter(counter) '.';
    text-align: right;
    width: var(--spacing-08)
}

ul {
    gap: var(--spacing-02);
    padding: 0;
}

ul li {
    padding-left: var(--spacing-08);
    list-style: none;
}

ul li:before {
    content: '—';
    opacity: 0.24
}

figure {
    margin-top: var(--spacing-08);
    margin-left: calc(var(--spacing-04) * -1)
}

dl {
    font-feature-settings: 'case';
    font-size: var(--desktop-body);
    line-height: var(--lh-desktop-body);
    margin-top: var(--spacing-04)
}

dl dt {
    font-weight: 600
}

dl dd {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
}

form {
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-13);
    position: relative;
    user-select: none;
    -ms-user-select: none;
    -webkit-user-select: none
}

form aside {
    display: flex;
    position: relative
}

form aside fieldset {
    display: flex;
    left: 0;
    position: absolute;
    padding: var(--spacing-00);
    width: 100%;
}

input {
    background-color: var(--background);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-muted);
    border-radius: var(--spacing-03);
    width: calc(var(--spacing-17) * 3);
    -webkit-appearance: none;
    -moz-appearance: none;
    appearance: none;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    flex: 1;
    padding: var(--spacing-03) var(--spacing-05);
}

input ::placeholder {
    color: var(--text-placeholder)
}

input:hover {
    border-color: var(--border)
}

input:focus {
    border-color: var(--border);
    outline: 1px solid var(--order-focus);
    outline-offset: 0
}

.button {
    background: var(--button);
    border-radius: var(--spacing-02);
    font-family: system-ui, sans-serif;
    color: var(--text-on-color);
    cursor: pointer;
    display: inline-flex;
    font-weight: 600;
    padding: 0.25em 1.3em;
    text-decoration: none;
    white-space: nowrap;
    align-items: center;
    position: inherit;
    top: var(--spacing-02);
    right: var(--spacing-02);
    height: 32px;
}

.button:hover {
    background: var(--button-hover)
}

.button:active {
    background: var(--button-active)
}

a {
    font-weight: 600;
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-decoration-thickness: 0.06em;
    text-underline-offset: 0.1em;
    color: var(--link);
}

a:hover {
    color: var(--link-hover);
}

a:visited {
    color: var(--link-visited);
}

b,
strong {
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: normal;
}

i,
em {
    font-style: italic;
}

@media (max-width: 50rem) {

    header,
    main {
        padding-left: var(--spacing-09, 2em);
        padding-right: var(--spacing-09, 2em);
    }
    main form aside fieldset input {
      width: 100%;
    }
    .button {
      top: var(--spacing-02);
      right: var(--spacing-02);
      height: 30px;
    }
}
</style>
